The common short name of the desktop environment
desk_name="XFCE4"

A long description
desk_desc="The Cholesterol Free Desktop Environment"

The command to execute
desk_comd="/usr/bin/startxfce4"

Arguments to desk_comd
desk_opts=""

Prefix for session manager (exec $desk_sess $desk_comd $desk_opts)
desk_sess="ck-launch-session dbus-launch --exit-with-session"

Prefix without session manager (exec $desk_norm $desk_comd $desk_opts)
desk_norm="dbus-launch --exit-with-session"

[Optional]
Use script to initialize before run.
if desk_prep = 1 then runs conf file with parameter "prepare".
This is used by wmaker to run wmaker.inst. Default is 0.
desk_prep={0|1}
